Yeah,as you see,this is a interface that making you connenting everything by usb.And it's not totally usb-driver.

For example,u have a mouse connecting to your computer by usb-port, u want to control your stupidphone by moving your smartmouse.At this monmont,this interface can help u.Also if u want to play a game using your phone to control and the PC deal with data and show graphic.This interface also can be used.
All in one,this interface is to provide a method that making everything can control or recive something sended by another one.If u want to do this with me,just clone the repository.
